name: [JIUN] [HOST COMMUNITY/OPS] - Trigger warning for Host self deliver as Dasher

parameters.query:
SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct b.id as booking_id,
b.ref_no, b.status, 
b.created_at, 
l.user_id as host_id, 
u.email as host_email, 
u.uuid as host_uuid
from bookings b
left join listing_location ll on ll.listing_id = b.listing_id
left join listings l on l.id = b.listing_id
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
where 1=1
--and b.status = 'accepted'
and ll.country = 'Malaysia'
and b.ref_no = 'YQ7VJ97U'
--and b.created_at >= NOW() - interval '14 day'

select distinct dt.reference_id::numeric, 
dt.type,
dt.status,
dt.assigned_to
from tasks dt
where dt.client = 'trevo'
and dt.status not in ('cancelled')
and dt.reference_id = '{{ $json.booking_id }}'
